      • forType

        public static HspBuilder<?,?,?> forType(String type)
        Create a new HspBuilder instance for the given type by name ("blastn", "blastp" etc).
        Parameters:
        type - the name of the type, case-insensitive; can not be null.
        Returns:
        a new HspBuilder will never be null.
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - if type is null.
        IllegalArgumentException - if type is not equal-ignoring-case with "blastn", "blastp", "blastx", "tblastn", or "tblastp".
